summary:
An honest, proactive, flexible and focused individual with more than 20 years’ experience in supporting organizational change within international client service organizations. 
An enthusiastic team player who is adaptable and supportive as well as being empathetic and passionate about people.
Willing and eager to learn and take on new challenges.   
I am also determined to create a positive working experience across the employee lifecycle
